        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Director', 3: 'Don\\'t be so naive!', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 83,
        "ActionId": 84,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The director pounds his cane. After a moment of silence is restored in the room, the old man sighs and opens his mouth.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 84,
        "ActionId": 85,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 85,
        "ActionId": 86,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '2', 2: '14'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 86,
        "ActionId": 87,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Director', 3: 'I know what you\\'ve been doing to help, but it\\'s pointless.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 87,
        "ActionId": 88,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Director', 3: 'Even our regulars can\\'t convince their children at home to come. Do you think putting up posters will convince hoodlums to come and pay to see our plays?', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 88,
        "ActionId": 89,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 204,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '14'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 89,
        "ActionId": 90,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Changyu', 3: 'But...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 90,
        "ActionId": 91,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Laoyu', 3: 'Y-you\\'re right, Director. W-we haven\\'t had a play in t-two months.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 91,
        "ActionId": 92,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Changyu', 3: 'Where there\\'s a will, there\\'s a way! You taught me that!', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 92,
        "ActionId": 93,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Changyu', 3: 'We\\'ve been performing for years. We can\\'t just call it quits like that!', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 93,
        "ActionId": 94,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Director', 3: 'If we quit now, we can do it with our heads held high. Selling the theater should be enough for a fresh start for each and every one of us.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 94,
        "ActionId": 95,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Director', 3: 'If we wait this out, then... There won\\'t be any money to line our pockets.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 95,
        "ActionId": 96,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Changyu\\'s face turns sour. People used to fear the stubborn and arrogant director. But with the steady decline of the troupe, his hardiness malformed into something pathetic. That is what unsettles Changyu the most.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 96,
        "ActionId": 97,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Director', 3: 'I\\'ve also considered who will take over the theater—a member of the Chiwen Crew. They\\'ve offered a fair price.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 97,
        "ActionId": 98,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Director', 3: '...If this truly is the end, I\\'ll at least be able to say that we\\'re even.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 98,
        "ActionId": 99,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 202,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '2', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 99,
        "ActionId": 100,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The director rubs the wooden handle of the chair begrudgingly. In his mind, the theater is a living thing.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 100,
        "ActionId": 101,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'But alas, some things must be put out of their misery, and he had to be the one to end it.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 101,
        "ActionId": 102,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'The director stands there in silence. The fatigue seems to have taken on an almost age-long pallor. No one knows how to console him.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 102,
        "ActionId": 103,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'And so everyone stands there as well, in solemn silence.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 103,
        "ActionId": 104,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500230', 3: '14', 4: '-400'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 104,
        "ActionId": 105,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '2', 2: '500229', 3: '14', 4: '400'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 105,
        "ActionId": 106,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Director', 3: 'Changyu, you\\'re no longer a child. Even if you leave the theater, you should have other ways to support yourself.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 106,
        "ActionId": 107,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Changyu', 3: '...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 107,
        "ActionId": 108,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Laoyu', 3: 'D-D-Director...'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 108,
        "ActionId": 109,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Changyu', 3: 'If there\\'s another way... A better way...', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 109,
        "ActionId": 110,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Director', 3: 'Let this be the end.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 110,
        "ActionId": 111,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Director', 3: 'These ol\\' bones aren\\'t what they used to be. Maybe it\\'s not necessarily a bad thing that I end it here.', 4: '2'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 111,
        "ActionId": 112,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 202,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '2', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 112,
        "ActionId": 113,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'Everyone is overcome with silence seeing the director lean dejectedly on his chair. They want to keep living the life they have had—they just cannot.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 113,
        "ActionId": 114,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{3: 'They all know that his old and feeble body has paid a heavy toll trying to hold up this fizzling dream. They even begin to think that it would be best to relieve him of this responsibility.'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 114,
        "ActionId": 115,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{2: 'Laoyu', 3: 'If... If we can just m-make it through this month...'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 115,
        "ActionId": 116,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 201,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: '500230', 3: '5'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 116,
        "ActionId": 117,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 301,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 2: 'Changyu', 3: 'There must be another way. I\\'ll think of something!', 4: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 117,
        "ActionId": 118,
        "NextActionId": null,
        "Type": 202,
        "IsBlock": null,
        "IsEnd": null,
        "BeginAnim": null,
        "EndAnim": null,
        "BeginDelay": null,
        "EndDelay": null,
        "Params": "{1: '1', 6: '1'}"
    },
    {
        "Id": 118,
        "ActionId": 119,
